{"word":"G829 - αὐθάδης - authádēs - ow-thad'-ace - Self-willed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αὐθάδης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">authádēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ow-thad'-ace</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Self-willed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தன் இஷ்டப்படி செய்யும், அகங்கார - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"self - pleasing, self - willed, arrogant"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G846 - αὐτός - autós - ow-tos'/846\">G846</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2237 - ἡδονή - hēdonḗ - hay-don-ay'/2237\">G2237</a>; <i>self pleasing</i>, that is, <i>arrogant:</i> - self-willed.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}